<view class="page">
  <view class="nav">
    <view class="back" bindtap="onBack">‹</view>
    <text>笔迹分析结果</text>
  </view>

  <view class="summary-card">
    <image class="summary-art" src="../../assets/images/feature-handwriting.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <view class="summary-copy">
      <text class="kicker">AI 分析完成</text>
      <text class="summary-title">当前状态：整体平稳</text>
      <text class="summary-desc">书写结构清晰，节奏略快，提示近期可能存在轻度压力与专注消耗。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="score-badge">
      <text>78</text>
      <text>分</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-title">
      <view></view>
      <text>书写特征</text>
    </view>
    <view class="trait-grid">
      <view class="trait-item" wx:for="{{traits}}" wx:key="label">
        <text class="trait-value">{{item.value}}</text>
        <text class="trait-label">{{item.label}}</text>
        <text class="trait-status">{{item.status}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-title">
      <view></view>
      <text>状态解读</text>
    </view>
    <view class="result-list">
      <view class="result-row" wx:for="{{detailRows}}" wx:key="name">
        <text>{{item.name}}</text>
        <text>{{item.value}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-title">
      <view></view>
      <text>调养建议</text>
    </view>
    <view class="advice-list">
      <view class="advice-row" wx:for="{{advice}}" wx:key="title">
        <text class="advice-title">{{item.title}}</text>
        <text class="advice-text">{{item.text}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice">
    <text>笔迹分析仅作健康管理参考，不构成医学诊断或治疗建议。如持续不适，请及时咨询专业医生。</text>
  </view>

  <button class="bottom-btn" bindtap="onAgain">重新分析</button>
</view>
